that’s a wrap on season 1 of Dress Code 👩🏻‍💻⭐️ Thank you to everyone who watched, commented, and discussed!!!!! I always dreamed of having my own show when I was little, but as I got older I became scared of video because of how much harder it is to hide the things you’re insecure about. It made me feel so exposed and I don’t think I was ready to let that image of myself go until now. Thank u to all the sweet tech bros who let me into their closets and had such a great sense of humor around it all ⭐️🥺🍒🍀
